text: Alexus Laird (born 11 March 1993) is a Seychellois swimmer. At the 2016 Summer Olympics she competed in the Women’s 100 m backstroke. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Olympic swimmers of Seychelles Category:1993 births Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:African Games bronze medalists for Seychelles Category:African Games medalists in swimming Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games Category:Female backstroke swimmers
